                           2. <quote>Simon Wilthart, statrichter ze Neumburg chlosterhalben</quote>,
                           3. <quote>Hans der Plodel, die des tags geding gewesen sind</quote>. </p></seal></sealDesc></physDesc></msDesc></sourceDesc></fileDesc><encodingDesc><projectDesc default="false"><p><label type="contentual-editing">Projekt Christina Lutter Stadt und Gemeinschaft</label></p></projectDesc></encodingDesc><profileDesc><creation>
